title: Law of attra
description:
I made this for myself and have decided to share it from the principle of "if i want it, odds are good that others do too".

It's a mix of a few paraliminals with some relaxing background music.

The paraliminals are:
Jack Canfield - Effortless succcess, all 3 sessions - Ask, Believe, Receive
Self esteem supercharger
Prosperity
and I think Bob Proctor's Power thinking aswell, but I can't remember.

Just so we're clear, this is a single mp3 file, a mix of several paraliminals. It's NOT separate sessions. Plus, there's no relaxation exercises.

I wanted something for night time use, something I could have on repeat. Here it is.

Enjoy!
